[h3 id=AdoptTheOrphans 
	" Adopt the orphans
	$LF
]h3
[ul 
	[li 
		" The 
		(__wikiLink|href=/WikiOrphans|implicitdisplaytext=Wiki Orphans)
		" page contains pages with no links to them. To make these pages findable, links to them should be added on relevant pages. This is an ongoing problem.  It is HIGHLY encouraged that all staff & editors participate in keeping these Orphans fixed.
		$LF
		[ul 
			[li 
				" Wiki orphans also track links non-existent pages linked from somewhere else on the site. Often this indicates brackets were intended for another purpose but got interpreted by the wiki engine as a link. This can be fixed by changing 
				[code 
					"[Text in brackets]
				]code
				" to 
				[code 
					"[[Text in brackets]]
				]code
				" (see 
				(__wikiLink|href=/TextFormattingRules#ReferencesLinks|implicitdisplaytext=TextFormattingRules#ReferencesLinks)
				" for more details). Alternatively, if it was intended to be a link, the link can be corrected to link to an existing page or a new page can be created at the link.
				$LF
			]li
		]ul
	]li
]ul
[h3 id=PagesNeeded 
	" Pages needed
	$LF
]h3
[ul 
	[li 
		"Write missing pages (
		(__wikiLink|href=/LawsOfTAS|implicitdisplaytext=LawsOfTAS)
		") detailing the implementation of rerecording, from a coding perspective.  This needs to include movie format specifications, including pros and cons of various methods already tried.  Also should include the "bullet proof" rerecording logic.  All aspects that are required for TASVideos acceptance should be explained clearly as well as detailing how to achieve these results.  
		$LF
	]li
]ul
